
Overview of noun communion

The noun communion has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (4) Communion, Holy Communion, sacramental manduction, manduction -- (the act of participating in the celebration of the Eucharist; "the governor took Communion with the rest of the congregation")
2. (3) communion, sharing -- (sharing thoughts and feelings)
3. communion -- ((Christianity) a group of Christians with a common religious faith who practice the same rites)
